data.description: Quiet home situated on 2 acres of land with large wired 3 stahl barn and tack room/ fenced pasture area including drive through gate and walk through gate. Pasture has been plumbed for water - easy to take care of those horses, goats, and cows! Cozy home featuring vinyl plank flooring and original hardwoods, custom concrete flooring in master bathroom and wash room.  Two living spaces - great for entertaining! Grainite countertops, tile shower and so much more!  Sellers are related to listing agent.
